name: I JUMP TOO!
description:
brother has buried his brain again!

I have no idea where to look for it, and my fix has no effect...

and we're already LATE for WOO-WOO's birthday party!

gotta go like this!

AND FAST!

CONTROLS:

A and D - go left and right

SPACE - jump

ENTER - pick up / throw bro

R - Restart

N - Skip Level
